gained .30 to 149.97. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was up .54 at 299.62.
   On Thursday the Dow Jones industrial average dropped 11.56
points to 2,052.45.
   Declining issues outnumbered advances by about 3 to 2 on the
NYSE, with 582 up, 887 down and 482 unchanged. Big Board volume
totaled 193.54 million shares, down from 234.56 million in the
previous session.
